|               |                     CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |                       HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Inner, on=[(n_nationkey@0, s_nationkey@2)], projection=[n_name@1, n_regionkey@2, l_extendedprice@3, l_discount@4]                                                         |
