|               |                                   HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Inner, on=[(o_orderkey@1, l_orderkey@0)], projection=[c_nationkey@0, l_suppkey@3, l_extendedprice@4, l_discount@5]                                            |
|               |                                     CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                           |
